{"tid":2040472,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)追殺夏娃 Killing Eve","createTime":"2020-05-28T15:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T19:20:18.000Z","uid":29160,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8f04a24e97eb6bbcba73b744488505b73af64027","tid":2040472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:04:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新沙士已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">播唔完下次播返</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuyvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=c684f9ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuyvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=50bbb435\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuyvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=3d80afa8\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZDE0NTc0NjMtNDc2Mi00NTY2LWJiNTItNDBlOWQxMTM5ZmMyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzQ2MDI5NjU@._V1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.media-amazon.com%2Fimages%2FM%2FMV5BZDE0NTc0NjMtNDc2Mi00NTY2LWJiNTItNDBlOWQxMTM5ZmMyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzQ2MDI5NjU%40._V1_.jpg&h=06cae610&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://www.voguehk.com/media/2020/04/91045513_1440271496160034_8912050696749056000_o-1-1024x1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voguehk.com%2Fmedia%2F2020%2F04%2F91045513_1440271496160034_8912050696749056000_o-1-1024x1280.jpg&h=aa49f861&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《追殺夏娃》改編自盧克詹寧斯（Luke Jennings）的中篇小說，全八集由《倫敦生活》（Fleabag）編劇、主演菲比沃勒布里奇（Phoebe Waller-Bridge）主創，故事圍繞在兩名女人之間，一位是精神病態殺手，另一位則是追捕她的安全局職員<br />\n<br />\n隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuyvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=2355b4a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuyvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=956cce1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cbadc80f403c822f854522a95e90b1f82025b28","tid":2040472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T15:18:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b016a884048eaa7e4a60083a4080006909baf4","tid":2040472,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2